thread.title: Judy
thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Judy

author: Judy
title: Judy
text: I was looking for a specific metal frame so I ordered a two samples that looked the closest match for what I needed. The samples arrived in good time. Unfortunately, once in hand I could see that the backside holding the hardware was narrower than what I was looking for. I thank them for the great service in getting the samples to me to verify it before placing an order that I could not use.
